? Novak partis. * Heind. for Cod. maaime (cp. Aul. Gell. xvi. 19, also of Arion, re bona multa), 3. Kussner for Cod. qui. But Mai says potiri may be auri_ in the Cod. Ἷ ὁ For Cod. sibi. 5 Cod. possiet.

