Ad M. Cass. iii. 17 (Naber, p. 55).

Have mi Fronto merito carissime. Intellego istam tuam argutissimam strofam, quam tu quidem benignissime repperisti; ut, quia 1 Query battwunt, of fencing. See Suet. Cal. 32; 54.

