May you keep your birthday, my master, both sound in health now and strong in all years to come, happy, and with all your wishes granted; which yearly prayer of mine grows ever more compre- hensive as my capacity for affection increases and the period of our most sweet intercourse lengthens ! Farewell, my master most delightfulto me. Mymother greets you. Give Gratia a greeting and your little Gratia a kiss from me.

